aryContaineruniface_104guj1665702720735.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/guj1665702720735.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/guj1665702720735.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"guj1665702720735\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Allow the use of Japanese Gaiji characters.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"guj1665702720735__topic_d140513e1_d140514e1_d140515e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"guj1665702720735__p_d140516e1_d140517e1_d140518e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$GAIJI</span>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">1</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"guj1665702720735__section_lkg_zpx_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1113582e68\">Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"guj1665702720735__ul_upf_1qx_bwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"guj1665702720735__li_d49724e1_d49725e1_d49726e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>—Japanese Gaiji characters are\n          enabled. The Unicode private area E000–F8FF is not available for other purposes, because\n          it is used for mapping the Gaiji characters. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"guj1665702720735__li_d49727e1_d49728e1_d49729e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>—Gaiji characters are disabled but\n          the Unicode private area E000–F8FF is available. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"guj1665702720735__section_g4n_zpx_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1113582e87\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"guj1665702720735__table_d17150e1_d17151e1_d17152e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Client assignment files </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[SETTINGS] </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528036\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528036\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$GAIJI Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 30, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Allow the use of Japanese Gaiji characters. $GAIJI { = } 1 | 0 Arguments 1 —Japanese Gaiji characters are enabled. The Unicode private area E000–F8FF is not available for other purposes, because it is used for mapping the Gaiji characters. 0 —Gaiji characters are disabled but the Unicode private area E000–F8FF is available. Defaults Assignment file: Client assignment files Section: [SETTINGS] Default value: 1 Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}